name: transport, freight train, electricity | transport, freight train | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/9688/documentation

Based on Swiss, Chinese and European electric freight train. The datasets represents the entire transport life cycle of an electric freight train.;[This dataset is meant to replace the following datasets:]

The dataset starts with the production of a locomotive.

Based on Swiss, Chinese and European electric freight train; it includes operation of electric freight train only. This dataset calls the modules 'production, maintenance of vehicle'; 'construction of railway track'.
